{"tid":1369426,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"下次應該帶支法蘭西王國國旗出黎","createTime":"2019-07-26T16:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T18:59:30.000Z","uid":254330,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d248df713442d7fae02a1fe1c5f3527320de0fc2","tid":1369426,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底點先可以象徵<span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span>呢？<br />\n每次都只係見到英國旗、香港旗、美國旗。btw 揸英國旗個婆婆真係好落力，好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> respect adore<br />\n<br />\n但如果講起<span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span>，最具象徵同代表性嘅應該係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">法蘭西王國</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Royaume des Fran&ccedil;ais</span></span><br />\n(1790年-1792年)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fBvKABX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfBvKABX.png&h=b82c496a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同目前嘅法國(法蘭西第五共和國)國旗係有分別嘅<br />\n<br />\n呢支旗嘅起源時間係1789年嘅法國大革命(French Revolution)，同時成為法蘭西王國(Royaume de France 1790-1792)及其後法蘭西第一共和國(R&eacute;publique fran&ccedil;aise)嘅國旗。<br />\n<br />\n之後，為左反波旁王朝國王查理十世(Charles X)，法國係1830年爆發七月革命(July Revolution、R&eacute;volution de Juillet)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2b2dt2y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2b2dt2y.png&h=585159e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARNpAHW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARNpAHW.png&h=f1e22938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個畫面相信大家都好熟悉，當中情節其實就係七月革命，用嘅都係呢支旗。<br />\n<br />\n1830年革命成功後，波旁王朝被推翻，法國人建立法蘭西王國(1830-1848)<br />\n國旗都係 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SuRE84r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuRE84r.png&h=454129d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n七月革命嘅成功，令當時係歐洲都非常流行嘅君主專制政權同封建制度完全收皮！另外，神職人員、貴族嘅特權都消失。<br />\n歷史總會係驚人的相似，我唔知香港嘅革命會帶來咩改變。但係，香港人仲未有革命嘅心！<br />\n<br />\n有睇過Les Mis&eacute;rables(孤星淚)嘅都可能留意到，其實法國咁多次革命之中都唔係每個人都同意/肯接受。當中仲有好多人趁機賺錢、混入革命隊伍做內鬼、話影響到自己生活所以反對... <span style=\"color: red;\">err... 點解同香港有d似</span><br />\n<br />\nFinally 呢支旗象徵著法國大革命，具有非常強烈嘅革命意識。<br />\n依家，呢支旗就代表<span style=\"color: red;\">自由、平等、博愛</span><br />\n個人對呢類歷史都只係有基本了解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錯唔該指正同屌細力少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望下次可以見到呢支旗周街都係！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"062251fcbd02e19b1200dd89271216b9fa58794f","tid":1369426,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"Do you hear the people sing?<br />\nSinging the songs of angry men?<br />\nIt is the music of the people<br />\nWho will not be slaves again!"},{"pid":"59a8d6abed7eddcb55a1915c0c4a118a1e2c8720","tid":1369426,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B29O2yb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB29O2yb.png&h=8129b60f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56a7c88433bf3bcc92ca96c16b30b7d73675dd20","tid":1369426,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:51:22.000Z","msg":"可唔可以拎漢旗"},{"pid":"502950fc7ee63644c9dc89a437cc74f3c6a1e393","tid":1369426,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:57:25.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"7f04b8ef05317720ef86a8f884b2c2aaa0ef5aa1","tid":1369426,"uid":254330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:03:35.000Z","msg":"Free Hong Kong ！"},{"pid":"dfd582568ad43161f5916b08e55e866612e40ade","tid":1369426,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:42:34.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"76c1f95907e4694c1a26e74b606c88ed7faee4bf","tid":1369426,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:59:30.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"}]}